                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050710-45-off257 t18050710-45-cd258"></join>, twenty-two yards of Irish linen, value 50 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18050710-45-victim504" type="victimName">
